0.1.name: wordpress/corpo
0.1.description: Corpo is a responsive business & portfolio theme which can be used for personal or corporate website. It features slider on the home page, 5 custom widgets, 2 menu locations and theme options to easily manage your website. Corpo also offers additional Portfolio custom post type  to showcase your work.
